📊 Sales Analysis SQL Project
📌 Project Overview

This project demonstrates basic to intermediate SQL operations using a Sales dataset. It covers data retrieval, filtering, sorting, and simple analysis queries.

🗂️ Database Schema
Table: Sales
Column Name	Data Type	Description
sale_id	INT (PK)	Unique sale ID
customer_name	VARCHAR(50)	Customer name
city	VARCHAR(50)	Customer city
product_name	VARCHAR(50)	Product purchased
category	VARCHAR(50)	Product category
quantity	INT	Quantity purchased
price	DECIMAL(10,2)	Price per product
sale_date	DATE	Date of sale
🛠️ Table Creation
CREATE TABLE Sales (
    sale_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50),
    city VARCHAR(50),
    product_name VARCHAR(50),
    category VARCHAR(50),
    quantity INT,
    price DECIMAL(10,2),
    sale_date DATE
);
